{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend the Warm House Discount criteria to cover all receiving benefits",
        "additional_details": "Many people have lost their Warm Home Discount due to the Winter 22/23 changes. Many people are no longer eligible to support of \u00a3150 towards our bills, that we cannot make up.",
        "background": "We would like the Government to extend the Warm Home Discount criteria to cover all receiving benefits, regardless of what benefits or energy efficiency rating they have. We would like all those on benefits to be entitled to this support.",
